  "name": "Intune Profile Bulk Renamer Tool",
  "description": "Intune Profile Bulk Renamer Tool is a self-contained PowerShell 7 + Windows Forms desktop app that connects to Microsoft Graph to bulk rename and re-describe Intune configuration profiles. It pulls multiple content types into an editable grid, supports inline edits, CSV export/import, and literal/regex Find & Replace; updates are applied as minimal PATCH requests only to changed items. Includes dry-run, JSON backups, automatic safety backups, and thorough logging.",
